FBIS4-5547 "dreas070_c_94050" FBIS-EAS-94-070 Daily Report 12 Apr 1994 North Korea Visitors Arriving in Pyongyang Noted Visitors Arriving in Pyongyang Noted SK1204052094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0431 GMT 12 Apr 94 SK1204052094 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, April 12 (KCNA) -- Shuhachi Inoue, director general of the International Institute of the Chuche Idea, arrived in Pyongyang on April 11. On the same day a delegation of old officials of the General Association of Korean Residents in Japan (Chongnyon) headed by Paek Chong-won, chairman of the Korean Physical Culture and Sports Federation in Japan, and a delegation of Korean Social Scientists in Japan headed by Pak Yong-kon, chairman of the Association of Korean Social Scientists in Japan, arrived in Pyongyang to visit the socialist homeland.
